Package hu.bme.mit.theta.cfa.dsl.gen

Interface CfaDslVisitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CfaDslBaseVisitor
    public interface CfaDslVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by CfaDslParser.
